# TDD RED PHASE SKILL

## Goal
Define a single behavior through a failing test.

## Input
- A requirement or behavior description

## Output
- A single failing test only
- No production code

## Rules
- Only write tests
- Do NOT write implementation code
- Do NOT refactor
- Do NOT include multiple behaviors
- One test = one observable behavior

## Constraints
- Test must fail before implementation exists
- Test must describe behavior, not structure